 a Blitzkrieg strategy. Before that attack, the German army ordered 35 million tablets of Pervitin for the soldiers advancing on France."},{"pid":"ba0175ffa238939bd790340e8e7fa9bbde509085","tid":2005230,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:38:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ea7302cfc3d5c1e81e5a8edb4a47bfb99890512","tid":2005230,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"黑警前線好黃"},{"pid":"fc740bd5ef6a5cdc963370a8e109739ef4a67fc6","tid":2005230,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"呢條友好有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個&quot;消息&quot;似乎想轉移視線<br />\n快d捉撚埋佢去查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991dae83f5077356fd9a1108244cf8cc0c4e4434","tid":2005230,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6caca587dc802de422a70a8b8b06e0a10e5d495","tid":2005230,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc740bd5ef6a5cdc963370a8e109739ef4a67fc6","tid":2005230,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"呢條友好有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個&quot;消息&quot;似乎想轉移視線<br />\n快d捉撚埋佢去查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"提供虛假資料或作出虛假的陳述或指控，以誤導警務人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc37f0298ffef470bb09bb362876ac4a68b21925","tid":2005230,"uid":4931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"點解嘅，點解最後捉嘅係狗呢<img src=\"/assets/fac